parameters.name: EndDate
parameters.description: End date of the query. The format is a Unix timestamp, in milliseconds.

parameters.name: HasDeviceRisk
parameters.description: Whether there is device risk (pass true if root = 1 or simulator = 1 or virtual_video = 1).

parameters.name: OuterOrderNo
parameters.description: Unique identifier for the customer request.

parameters.name: Passed
parameters.description:
Whether the authentication passed:
- **T**: Passed
- **F**: Not passed

parameters.name: Root
parameters.description: Whether it is rooted (pass 1 if selected, otherwise do not pass; corresponds to identity label risk type).

parameters.name: Simulator
parameters.description: Whether it is a simulator (pass 1 if selected, otherwise do not pass; corresponds to device label risk type).

parameters.name: SubCode
parameters.description: Result Code. For detailed values, please refer to: [SubCode Explanation](https://help.aliyun.com/zh/id-verification/financial-grade-id-verification/error-code-person-verify?spm=a2c4g.11186623.0.0.6015566ebArcFw#d88910e172fgg).

parameters.name: SubCodes
parameters.description: Comma-separated Result Codes. For detailed values, please refer to: [SubCode Explanation](https://help.aliyun.com/zh/id-verification/financial-grade-id-verification/error-code-person-verify?spm=a2c4g.11186623.0.0.6015566ebArcFw#d88910e172fgg).

parameters.name: VirtualVideo
parameters.description: Whether it is a virtual adaptation (pass 1 if selected, otherwise do not pass; corresponds to behavior label risk type).
